# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:213
translate spanish connie15_596c0f44:

    # con "You know, besides my husband, you're the first man I've had sex with in fifty years."
    con "Sabes, aparte de mi marido, eres el primer hombre con el que me he acostado en cincuenta años."

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:214
translate spanish connie15_6a75940e:

    # pc "Really? You and Jackson never had anything?"
    pc "¿En serio? ¿Tú y Jackson nunca tuvisteis nada?"

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:215
translate spanish connie15_03c8c55b:

    # con "Naw, he's like a brother to me. He's never looked at me like that."
    con "No, él es como un hermano para mí. Nunca me ha mirado así."

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:216
translate spanish connie15_42e3bab3:

    # con "Nobody ever really looks at me like that."
    con "Nadie me mira así, la verdad."

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:219
translate spanish connie15_bab07018:

    # pc "I don't see why not. You're a good looking woman."
    pc "No veo por qué no. Eres una mujer guapa."

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:220
translate spanish connie15_2a7d9ea2:

    # con "I try, but nobody is interested in an old lady."
    con "Lo intento, pero a nadie le interesa una anciana."

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:221
translate spanish connie15_f0f40b8d:

    # con "You got to use it while you're young, you know? Else you end up stuck in an old body, all alone."
    con "Hay que aprovecharlo mientras se es joven, ¿sabes? Si no, acabas atrapada en un cuerpo viejo, completamente sola."

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:222
translate spanish connie15_007fbff2:

    # pc "You have regrets?"
    pc "¿Te arrepientes de algo?"

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:223
translate spanish connie15_79491ffd:

    # con "Oh, no. Not really."
    con "Oh, no. La verdad es que no."

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:224
translate spanish connie15_bf42fbfd:

    # con "My husband was good to me. We had a lot of really good years."
    con "Mi marido me trataba bien. Pasamos muchos años muy buenos juntos."

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:227
translate spanish connie15_8fb15acf:

    # con "And that man was just as gifted as you are in bed."
    con "Y ese hombre era tan dotado como tú en la cama."

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:228
translate spanish connie15_acf7a854:

    # con "God, I miss him."
    con "Dios, cómo le echo de menos."

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:231
translate spanish connie15_25ac1736:

    # pc "Did you have any children?"
    pc "¿Tuviste hijos?"

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:232
translate spanish connie15_4575dead:

    # con "One. A boy. Chase."
    con "Uno. Un chico. Chase."

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:233
translate spanish connie15_5b0fb844:

    # con "He died over in Afghanistan."
    con "Murió en Afganistán."

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:234
translate spanish connie15_6c6d9416_1:

    # pc "Oh, I'm sorry."
    pc "Oh, lo siento."

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:237
translate spanish connie15_0fa6aba4_1:

    # con "It's okay."
    con "No pasa nada."

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:238
translate spanish connie15_d075efd8:

    # con "Sometimes I feel like I died too..."
    con "A veces siento como si yo también hubiera muerto..."

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:239
translate spanish connie15_454cba6d:

    # con "... and I'm just stuck here, waiting for my turn to go meet them."
    con "... y simplemente estoy atrapada aquí, esperando mi turno para ir a reunirme con ellos."

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:242
translate spanish connie15_19979052:

    # con "Thank you for making me feel alive for a little while."
    con "Gracias por hacerme sentir viva por un rato."

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:243
translate spanish connie15_2911487b:

    # con "You're a good kid."
    con "Eres un buen chico."

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:246
translate spanish connie15_109a5d63:

    # con "I think you and Brandi make a very nice couple."
    con "Creo que tú y Brandi hacéis una pareja muy bonita."

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:247
translate spanish connie15_68f01008:

    # con "You should consider settling down with her."
    con "Deberías plantearte sentar cabeza con ella."

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:248
translate spanish connie15_19e05b84:

    # con "I see you coming into Jackson's with different girls."
    con "Te veo venir a Jackson's con chicas diferentes."

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:249
translate spanish connie15_fedfc4a9:

    # con "You're young. That's a good thing. Experiment."
    con "Eres joven. Eso es algo bueno. Experimenta."

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:250
translate spanish connie15_ec119d97:

    # con "But eventually, I hope you'll pick a girl and start a life and a family with her."
    con "Pero, con el tiempo, espero que elijas a una chica y formes una vida y una familia con ella."

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:251
translate spanish connie15_1dc28a58:

    # con "And I hope you'll make each other very happy."
    con "Y espero que os hagáis muy felices el uno al otro."

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:252
translate spanish connie15_a40b7cd5:

    # pc "Thanks, Connie."
    pc "Gracias, Connie."

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:253
translate spanish connie15_0fd31492:

    # con "All right, that's enough reminiscing. Time to get dressed."
    con "Bueno, ya basta de recuerdos. Es hora de vestirse."

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:256
translate spanish connie15_2f1120e6:

    # "Before I leave, she hands me a tin full of chocolate chip cookies."
    "Antes de irme, me entrega una lata llena de galletas con trocitos de chocolate."

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:257
translate spanish connie15_189fa119:

    # con "I made these for Jackson, but he can have the next batch. You enjoy. You earned them."
    con "Las hice para Jackson, pero él puede quedarse con la próxima tanda. Disfrútalas. Te las has ganado."

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:258
translate spanish connie15_25e0f073:

    # con "Thanks again for making my day."
    con "Gracias de nuevo por alegrarme el día."

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:259
translate spanish connie15_a351accf:

    # con "I don't think we'll do this again, but I'm glad to have spent some time with you."
    con "No creo que volvamos a hacer esto, pero me alegro de haber pasado un rato contigo."

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:260
translate spanish connie15_a9da76fd:

    # pc "Me too, Connie."
    pc "Yo también, Connie."

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:261
translate spanish connie15_c6512378:

    # con "You take care."
    con "Cuídate."

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:264
translate spanish connie15_18c0b69c:

    # "I leave Connie's house and drive away."
    "Salgo de la casa de Connie y me alejo en coche."

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:265
translate spanish connie15_313c822e:

    # "I hope she'll be okay. She's a sweet lady."
    "Espero que ella esté bien. Es una mujer encantadora."

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:266
translate spanish connie15_f74a794a:

    # "And she gives a killer gummer."
    "Y da unos besos de muerte."

